INSTALL - A short installation documentation on HOWTO build thinstation

1. perform a clean github checkout of hzdr/thinstation:

   > git clone https://github.com/hzdr/thinstation.git thinstation-hzdr

2. prepare the setup chroot environment

   > cd thinstation-hzdr
   > sudo ./setup-chroot

3. run the build and automatically install the pxe images

   > ./mkhzdr
